<objective>
Create weather grid mapping system that reduces ~300 CTA stations to ~50 weather grid points, and integrate TTL caching with existing API modules for stations and track geometry.

Purpose: Preserve Open-Meteo 10k/day rate limit by consolidating weather requests to grid points while maintaining spatial coverage across Chicago transit system.
Output: Weather grid generator, cached API wrappers for stations/track geometry, and station→grid point mapping.
</objective>

